  , issueBody =
      Just
        "Split points should be chosen by the following procedure:\n- When the user writes to `rethinkdb.table_config`, it should keep the old split points if the number of shards has not changed.\n- If the number of shards has changed, it should run a distribution query to generate split points.\n- If the distribution query fails, it should estimate new split points using the old split points.\n- We should expose `r.table_rebalance()`, which should pick new split points using a distribution query. If the distribution query fails, it should give the user an error.\n"
